# Audio files directory

Place your audio files here for Billy to use.

Recommended formats:
- MP3 (best compatibility)
- WAV (best quality)
- OGG (good compression)

Example structure:
```
audio/
  welcome.mp3
  modules/
    m1-intro.mp3
    m1-complete.mp3
    m2-intro.mp3
    m2-complete.mp3
  quiz/
    correct.mp3
    incorrect.mp3
  encouragement/
    great-job.mp3
    keep-going.mp3
```

Tips:
- Keep files under 2MB each
- Use 128-192 kbps bitrate
- Keep messages under 15 seconds
- Use consistent volume levels

